headline: Visa to Announce Fiscal First Quarter 2026 Financial Results on January 29, 2026
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, January 15, 2026--Visa (NYSE: V) will report its fiscal first quarter 2026 financial results on Thursday, January 29, 2026. After market close, Visa will furnish the results with the Securities and Exchange Commission and post them, along with accompanying financial information, on the Visa Investor Relations website. Visa will issue a news wire alert when the earnings materials are publicly available, including a link to those documents.

headline: Mastercard, Visa and Revolut lose UK legal challenge over card fees
summary: Investing.com -- Mastercard, Visa and British fintech Revolut lost a legal challenge on Thursday against Britain’s payments regulator over its plans to cap cross-border card fees.
